            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I am happy to tackle the screen size problem.\n\nThere seems to have been a previous attempt to tackle this in https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/28621, with one of the main problems being that it reports the size of the `--headless` instance when run with `--remote-ui`. I've reproduced the issue and open a PR as soon as I fixed it.",
